    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>UNPUNISHED</strong> - A true horror for those who like to tickle nerves.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u></u><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/0407bd174dc6b9814b76b727e78382ff.avif?t=1744367832\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras_big/0407bd174dc6b9814b76b727e78382ff.avif?t=1744367832 width=800 height=292 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>«Who walks at night in the silence of the dead. <br>Hiding in shadows and gliding through foul rows. <br>He brings with death his discontent. <br>And secretly torments us from all sides in our dreams.»</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Average time to complete the game: 1 hour</u><i></i></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/c925f74f6ad65b1b1899c948c90663ad.poster.avif?t=1744367832\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/c925f74f6ad65b1b1899c948c90663ad.webm?t=1744367832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/c925f74f6ad65b1b1899c948c90663ad.mp4?t=1744367832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLOT SUMMARY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Back at home, Mark is immersed in memories of his childhood full of secrets. He was always afraid of the nights spent in his room, where a strange silhouette appeared every night. Only when he was given to his grandmother, Mark began to realize that his parents were hiding a lot. As he gradually unravels the secrets of the mansion, he begins to realize that his family is intertwined with mystical mysteries that lead to forbidden places from his childhood.</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Part of the mansion is built on simple riddles that open the way to places that Mark was forbidden to go to in his youth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/ba3dad35a9c27fbdc3c32a6c671ebd12.poster.avif?t=1744367832\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/ba3dad35a9c27fbdc3c32a6c671ebd12.webm?t=1744367832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/ba3dad35a9c27fbdc3c32a6c671ebd12.mp4?t=1744367832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT DOES THE GAME OFFER?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spooky atmosphere of an almost abandoned mansion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting plot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Possibility to stay alive</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game is made on the Unreal Engine 5 engine;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The gameplay is closer to realism;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Walking Simulator / Horror genre;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore an abandoned mansion;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find out what happened to the main character's family;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unravel the mysteries and secrets of the mansion and its past inhabitants;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The soundtrack will immerse you in the world of “UNPUNISHED”</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/3295c9bb9c53861c206e9777f0a1eb15.poster.avif?t=1744367832\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/3295c9bb9c53861c206e9777f0a1eb15.webm?t=1744367832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307980/extras/3295c9bb9c53861c206e9777f0a1eb15.mp4?t=1744367832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
